es/2014/3/24/1395673267300/Summerhill-school-002.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Ed Thompson","altText":"Summerhill school","height":"340","credit":"Ed Thompson","caption":"Neill’s ‘self-constructed, child-centred universe’ … Summerhill. Photograph: Ed Thompson","width":"480"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Books/Pix/pictures/2014/3/24/1395673268889/Summerhill-school-003.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Ed Thompson","altText":"Summerhill school","height":"130","credit":"Ed Thompson","caption":"Neill’s ‘self-constructed, child-centred universe’ … Summerhill. Photograph: Ed Thompson","width":"140"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Books/Pix/pictures/2014/3/24/1395673270444/Summerhill-school-004.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Ed Thompson","altText":"Summerhill school","height":"84","credit":"Ed Thompson","caption":"Neill’s ‘self-constructed, child-centred universe’ … Summerhill. Photograph: Ed Thompson","width":"140"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Books/Pix/pictures/2014/3/24/1395673271910/Summerhill-school-005.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Ed Thompson","altText":"Summerhill school","height":"132","credit":"Ed Thompson","caption":"Neill’s ‘self-constructed, child-centred universe’ … Summerhill. Photograph: Ed Thompson","width":"220"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Books/Pix/pictures/2014/3/24/1395673273627/Summerhill-school-006.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Ed Thompson","altText":"Summerhill school","height":"168","credit":"Ed Thompson","caption":"Neill’s ‘self-constructed, child-centred universe’ … Summerhill. Photograph: Ed Thompson","width":"280"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Books/Pix/pictures/2014/3/24/1395673275093/Summerhill-school-007.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Ed Thompson","altText":"Summerhill school","height":"18